column1: Supplementary Table S1: The collocation measurements between CTCF’s binding sites (CBF) and those binding sites of 1207 TFs curated in the ReMap database (https://remap.univ-amu.fr/). C, collocation coefficient;  J, the Jaccard coefficient; SD, the Sørensen-Dice coefficient; SS, the Szymkiewicz-Simpson coefficient; PMI, pointwise mutual information; NPMI, normalized pointwise mutual information. Zscore is the combinatorial score of J, SD, SS, PMI, and NPMI, measuring the overall cobindabilities between CTCF and other transcription factors.
